{
  "stem": "13911.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's true Very-- because they had to be-- being situated geographically between the two enemies who were always tearing Poland apart, they became very self-centered-- and, we Poles.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the Russians-- no, no, no-- a Pole wouldn't dare throwing a stone then, no.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After, they sent him-- because everybody had to do something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Russia, you didn't sit, and-- or your father would take care of you, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, let's say a student-- there was no-- everybody had to do their part.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was sent to a neighboring city, which was called Ustyluh, to work in the pharmacy there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is-- and he used to come in on the weekends.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he worked in Ustyluh.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was like until '41.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as I say, in 1941, when Germans attack again-- because now they have-- they so close.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now we are Russia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they are just next door to Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this was their aim, to capture Russia, especially starting with the Ukraine, the bread basket, the oil, I mean, all the riches, the natural resources.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so the war starts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my father is still there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And immediately, like, we-- we hear the heavy artillery, because we were just-- we were the beginning of the whole course-- and the artillery.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I remember my mother being frantic that my father is away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But he showed up the next day, I think, walking.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because there wasn't like, I'll take a train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I'll take a bus.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I'll take a car, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in any case, he showed up and came back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this was the beginning already of the tragic end-- the beginning, very beginning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Hitler attacks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They come in.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
